[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     81[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Finding 5: `expand_value_set` query uses `length(path)` which is deprecated in some openCypher implementations
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     82[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
