[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This matches the natural "ingest data, build graph, query graph" mental model. The decision to show the normalization query (Step 4) as the centerpiece, with hierarchy traversal and batch processing as extensions, is good pedagogy.
